{{DISPLAYTITLE:Level 11.9}}
<center><div class="light-borderblock" style="display: inline-block; width: 50%; font-family:Playwrite ZA">
Respite but not rest<br>
Fundamentally, you're merely a guest<br>
For they patch, but never mend<br>
In the dark tunnel, you'll see no end.

Their purpose is clear<br>
They do not want you here<br>
So where to go when not this place?<br>
To a sketchy zone where you're always chased.

Greed has corrupted them<br>
Leaving servitors with little income<br>
Increasingly distinct describes the divide<br>
But one day, the dam will subside.
</div></center>
<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>


