<div style="text-align:center; font-size:64px; color:#f8f6ee; text-shadow: 0px 0px 5.5px #e5d1db, 1px 4.5px 10px #684a6b, 1px 4.5px 10px #684a6b; font-family:Mozilla Headline;">"Where Every Block Carries Hate"</div></div>
